ygData.messageBody:
Yes, I am sorry to say that I switched to a High Elf Cleric. I have I think
85 str or something like that. I will hopefully do a lot better, and trust
me, CLERICS rule. hehe. Just thought I would say that. I love them. After
making 12 different characters, clerics have got to be the best. Everyone
have fun being a cleric!!

Adwen, High Elf Cleric
~Veeshan~

P.S. if you need banded and you are on my server, please give me a tell. I
have a master smith that is in the Freeport area and will gladly make yuo
banded armor. Medium right now, if I get molds I will reduce the price, and
make yuo whatever mold size you gave me.
